      "content": "i know i should talk to the doc but i have a super busy month coming up with work and i cant really make an appointment right now. i keep checking my blood and everything seems fine. if i'm already feeling so stable, isn't it pretty safe to just taper down a bit on my own? it's just a small adjustment, i'm not trying to stop it completely.",
